	<entry>
		<title>Embrace the Night (Part 1)</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-days-of-darkening/50-embrace-the-night/134-embrace-the-night-part-1"/>
		<published>2015-06-06T20:26:10+00:00</published>
		<updated>2015-06-06T20:26:10+00:00</updated>
		<id>https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-days-of-darkening/50-embrace-the-night/134-embrace-the-night-part-1</id>
		<author>
			<name>Kate Coady</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/background/authors-and-artists/132-tais-teng&quot;&gt;Tais Teng&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-days-of-darkening/134-embrace-the-night-part-1&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/teng-lesser-redoubt-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;A tall pyramidal tower, crowned with a green light, in a surreal dark landscape.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;The very second his nephew took his first breath the last star had winked out above the Redoubt...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</summary>
